trackName: Biquini de Bolinha Amarelinha Tão Pequeni…
lyrics:

E foi vestir um biquíni legal
Mas era tão pequenino o biquíni

Ai, ai, ai, mas ficou sensacional!

Ai, ai, ai, a garota tá pra mim!

imageDescription: A simple and creative image that represents the song "Itsy Bitsy Teenie Weenie Yellow Polkadot Bikini" is a close-up photograph of a small yellow polka dot bikini resting on the palm of a hand. The vibrant colors and tiny size of the bikini convey the playfulness and embarrassment of the song's lyrics, capturing the essence of Ana Maria's experience.
